//	StageType:
//		~ 1: Eliminations
//		~ 2: Semi-Finals
//		~ 3: Final
//
// ### TormentedSquare::EventMonsterAppearanceRate::Round ### - refers to EventMonsterSettings in IGC_TormentedSquare_Monsters.xml
